---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import sartorialMockup from "@/assets/images/sartorial-paris__mockup.webp";
---

<section
	class="w-10/12 md:w-3/5 mx-auto mt-20 md:mt-0 py-14 animate-fade-up animate-duration-700"
	id="about-me"
>
	<div class="w-full overflow-hidden">
		<Image
			src={sartorialMockup}
			alt="Sartorial Paris Homepage in a mockup"
			class="max-w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-lg shadow-xl"
		/>
	</div>
	<h1 class="text-2xl font-display mt-8 mb-10">
		Sartorial Paris - The Ultimate Menswear Destination
	</h1>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		I'm Ricardo, an enthusiastic <b class="font-textSemiBold"
			>Full-stack Developer</b
		> dedicated to crafting exceptional software solutions. My expertise lies
		in JavaScript development, where I blend technical precision with creative
		problem-solving.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		To me, software development is a craft that demands both technical
		excellence 🏅 and creative vision 🖼️.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		Every line of code is an opportunity to build something remarkable.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		I'm driven by the pursuit of <b class="font-textSemiBold"
			>Engineering Excellence 🧑🏽‍💻</b
		> and the satisfaction of creating elegant, efficient solutions.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		Over the past year, I've developed a specialization in Shopify
		development, drawn by its rich ecosystem in development and the exciting
		challenges of e-commerce businesses 🏬.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		My focus areas include <b class="font-textSemiBold"
			>Shopify Theme Development</b
		> and <b class="font-textSemiBold">Conversion Rate Optimization</b>,
		where I help transform online stores into high-performing digital
		experiences.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		I <b class="font-textSemiBold">Customize and Optimize 🎯</b> stores through
		a mastery of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Liquid (Shopify's Templating Language),
		crafting solutions that are both beautiful and functional.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		Though I'm proficient with modern frameworks like AlpineJS and
		TailwindCSS, I find particular value in the simplicity and reliability
		of vanilla Shopify themes.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		But I'll work with the tools that are best for the job.
	</p>
	<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
		In <b class="font-textSemiBold">Conversion Rate Optimization 📈</b>, I
		do <b class="font-textSemiBold">Conversion Design</b> and take a <b
			class="font-textSemiBold">Data-driven Approach</b
		>, utilizing advanced tools like heatmaps, scroll maps, and A/B testing
		to uncover insights and drive meaningful improvements. Every decision is
		backed by solid analytics and proven methodologies.
	</p>
</section>
